@StockService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5202

### Réserver du stock
POST {{StockService_HostAddress}}/stock/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "productId": "PROD-001",
  "quantity": 5
}

### Libérer du stock (compensation)
POST {{StockService_HostAddress}}/stock/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###
